line from the last report, which showed the same cron:6f3323ef job that was running around 21:05 UTC.\n\nLooking at the session details from that earlier report, all three cron jobs were running and healthy—the QLHV 5p monitor at about 88 minutes, the DTLX 5p monitor at 18 minutes, and the QLHV group session active. The telegram:direct session had completed normally around 20:32 UTC, and the group session wrapped up around 20:43 UTC. Now I need to check what's happened in the current cycle at 21:10 UTC. The cron:e7885813 session is still running with a 39-minute runtime since 21:04 UTC, and the group session remains active, so overall the system is stable with no new changes to report."},{"type":"text","text":"\nSilent. Comparing current state (21:10 UTC) against stored baseline (21:04 UTC):\n\n| Session | Baseline (21:04) | Current (21:10) | Δ |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p) | ✅ running | ✅ running | — |\n| `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV 5p) | ✅ running (~88m) | ✅ running | — |\n| `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status) | ✅ running (~39m) | ✅ running | — |\n| `telegram:group:-5163901258` | ✅ running | ✅ running (stale ~27m) | — |\n| `telegram:direct:6053576134` | ✅ done | ✅ done | — |\n| `main` | ✅ done | ✅ done | — |\n\nAll sessions stable. No failures, no blockers. Pipeline: HEALTHY. Silent."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":29245,"output":688,"totalTokens":44280,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":403,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776201085714,"responseId":"062de07f2f60826101fee1ddf447aa3c","__openclaw":{"id":"be8292a6","seq":5}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:6053576134","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776200764685,"sessi